
power systems optimization made beautiful
--------------------------------------------------------

* Solves :abbr:`ED (Economic Dispatch)`, :abbr:`OPF (Optimal Power Flow)`, and :abbr:`UC (Unit Commitment)` problems.
* Problems can be made in simple spreadsheets.
* Many `solvers <http://minpowertoolkit.com/solvers>`_ supported.

* `Full documentation and tutorials<http://minpowertoolkit.com/minpower>`_
* Actively developed on `GitHub <http://github.com/adamgreenhall/minpower>`_.
